- No `eval()` or dynamic code execution.
- No direct database queries (no SQL/NoSQL injection surface in current code).
- Hardcoded data is obviously placeholder; no real secrets or credentials visible.
- Clean module export pattern (`module.exports = app`) is test-friendly.

