| 🟠 High | No security headers | A05 | `helmet` |
| 🟠 High | No CORS policy | A05 | `cors` with allowlist |
| 🟠 High | No rate limiting | A04 | `express-rate-limit` |
| 🟠 High | No error handler (stack traces) | A05 | 4-arg error middleware |
| 🟡 Medium | Timestamp in `/health` | A05 | Remove or coarsen |
| 🟡 Medium | No body size limit | A04 | `express.json({ limit })` |
| 🟡 Medium | No logging/monitoring | A09 | `morgan` or `pino-http` |
| 🟡 Medium | No HTTPS | A02/A05 | TLS at proxy or in Node |

